{"tid":1358141,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"[繼續當集團專欄作家] 石鏡泉辭任經濟日報副社長及集團執董","createTime":"2019-07-24T01:05:45.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-24T03:25:35.000Z","uid":224066,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"234ba85b5eb7070c95dc766a668a7730dc95bbef","tid":1358141,"uid":224066,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-24T01:05:45.000Z","msg":"經濟日報副社長石鏡泉辭職，即時生效。<br />\n<br />\n石鏡泉於周六守護香港集會上，發表以籐條及水喉通教仔的言論。經濟日報的記者發表聯合聲明，譴責石鏡泉言論，意圖煽惑他人施暴行兇。石鏡泉其後發道歉聲明，撤回籐條及軟膠通的言論並致歉。<br />\n<br />\n經濟日報集團有限公司發通告，指石鏡泉因有意從事其他個人興趣，在星期一向董事會提出辭任公司執行董事及經濟日報副社長，董事會在星期二批准並即時生效，而石鏡泉將繼續當集團專欄作家。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn.thestandnews.com/media/photos/cache/shek-01_ULQc7_1200x0.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thestandnews.com%2Fmedia%2Fphotos%2Fcache%2Fshek-01_ULQc7_1200x0.png&h=44056b06&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"ea700e34bc92fa7122a65e174a5fe1dbee3ba6ac","tid":1358141,"uid":149978,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-24T03:19:05.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"25f808d9a9b55fa741ddec382f61778e3c0fd05e","tid":1358141,"uid":34047,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-24T03:25:35.000Z","msg":"呢條友直頭係發動緊恐怖襲擊"}]}